Package: ftirsr
Title: Easily load FTIR spectroscopy data for a Partial Least Squares Regression Model
Version: 0.0.0.9001
Authors@R: c(
    person("Emma", "Vejcik", email = "evejcik@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Grace", "Hartley", email = "grace.hartley@gmail.com", role = "aut")
    )
Maintainer: Emma Vejcik <evejcik@gmail.com>
Description: The `ftirsr` package works to faciliate Partial Least Squares (PLS) Regression with Fourier Transform Infrared (FTIR) spectroscopy data. This pacakge is designed to make it easy for geologists to create and optimize a PLS model to analyze the absorbance spectra of their data.
